description: Holly Heart has turned into a Brunette and her evil dark side has come out. She is a big bully on the mats today and she thinks her victim will be feather weight Champion, Mona Wales. Mona has been on a winning streak and she has been mean to her losing opponents. Today, one of these girls will get a dose of humility. Loser is Face fucked, fingered, choked, put into submissions over and over. Winner puts the Loser in the a tight head scissor and makes her submit
title: Holly Heart tries to bully Mona Wales. Some one gets Fucked
